# S3 access & features

## Pre-signed URLs

**Temporary, credential-free** access to one object; inherits the signer's rights, expires ≤ 7 days. For private-download links + **direct browser upload**.

## Access Points & events

- **Access Points** — named endpoints, **each with its own policy** (`analytics-ap`, `app-ap`, `vpc-ap`) vs. one tangled bucket policy
- **Event Notifications** — on create/remove/restore → **SQS / SNS / Lambda / EventBridge** (EventBridge once routing gets complex)

## Static website hosting

Direct `s3-website` endpoint for quick sites. **Production:** **CloudFront** in front → custom domain, **HTTPS (ACM)**, edge cache, **OAC** (bucket stays private) + WAF.
